<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id79fa3b9b-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s5012"><num value="5012">§ 5012.</num><heading> Disposition of property</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall dispose of any United States property held by the International North Pacific Fisheries Commission on the date of its termination in a manner that would further the purposes of this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id79fa3b9c-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/102/567/tVIII/s813">Pub. L. 102–567, title VIII, § 813</ref>, <date date="1992-10-29">Oct. 29, 1992</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/106/4316">106 Stat. 4316</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/102/587/tVIII/s8013">Pub. L. 102–587, title VIII, § 8013</ref>, <date date="1992-11-04">Nov. 4, 1992</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/106/5106">106 Stat. 5106</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/106/562/tIII/s304/a">Pub. L. 106–562, title III, § 304(a)</ref>, <date date="2000-12-23">Dec. 23, 2000</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/114/2806">114 Stat. 2806</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id79fa3b9d-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id79fa3b9e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="id79fa3b9f-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Title VIII of <ref href="/us/pl/102/567">Pub. L. 102–567</ref> and <ref href="/us/pl/102/587">Pub. L. 102–587</ref> enacted identical sections. Title VIII of <ref href="/us/pl/102/587">Pub. L. 102–587</ref> was repealed by <ref href="/us/pl/106/562">Pub. L. 106–562</ref>.</p>
</note>
